EOSPREFLIGHTAGENT(8) System Manager's Manual EOSPREFLIGHTAGENT(8)

NAME

eospreflightagent — iBridge software restore

DESCRIPTION

eospreflightagent is a system agent that opportunistically preflights iBridge software in the background to ensure a preflighted bundle exists for boot-time healing.

There are no configuration options to eospreflightagent, and users should not run eospreflightagent manually.

27/10/16 Mac OS X
